- {% for p in packages.split(",") %}`{{ p | trim }}/`{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %} — your package{% if packages.split(",")|length > 1 %}s{% endif %}. The guardrails target {% if packages.split(",")|length > 1 %}all of them{% else %}it{% endif %}; organise modules however the project needs.
